column2: SELECT s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, s.zErr, s.class, s.zWarning, s.snMedian,  zp.modelMag_u, zp.modelMag_g, zp.modelMag_r, zp.modelMag_i, zp.modelMag_z, (zp.modelMag_u-zp.modelMag_g) as u_g, (zp.modelMag_g-zp.modelMag_r) as g_r, (zp.modelMag_r-zp.modelMag_i) as r_i, (zp.modelMag_i-zp.modelMag_z) as i_z FROM SpecObjAll as s  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #, #) AS GN ON s.bestObjID = GN.objID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as zp ON zp.objID = s.bestObjID  WHERE  s.class = &&& AND   s.zWarning=# AND  (s.z > (AVG(s.z) - STDEV(s.z)))
